description:
&lt;p&gt;This post is only open to current employees of University Hospitals of Morecambe Bay.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A vacancy has arisen for a Colposcopy Administration Booking Clerk to be based at Furness General Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should be enthusiastic, well-motivated and able to work unsupervised. You will work closely with the Colposcopy co-ordinator, Consultants, Nurses and other Admin staff to ensure the smooth running of the Colposcopy Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of medical terminology and IT systems would be an advantage, although training will be given.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an ideal opportunity for personal development enabling the post holder to develop their skills and knowledge within this busy, but friendly environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anyone newly appointed to the trust will be subject to the completion of a satisfactory 6 month probationary period (this includes bank staff). This will give the new staff member an opportunity to become familiar with the role and working environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Namekarolina CzaplakJob titleColposcopy MDT co-ordinatorEmail addresskarolina.czaplak@mbht.nhs.ukTelephone number01229 403616&lt;/p&gt;
